Relasio
=======

Relasio is a Boost.Asio-based readline wrapper library.

Copyright (C) 2011  John Bytheway <jbytheway at that gmail place>

For building instructions see INSTALL.

Relasio contains the following components:

- relasio
  The library.

- test
  A small test app which mixes readline input and other asio events in one
  event loop.  Really more of a demo than a real test.


